---
/* CONTRACT: VIS overview for Article System v0.1; presentation layer only. */
import PrototypeLayout from "../../../../layouts/PrototypeLayout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<PrototypeLayout title="Article System">
  <main class="px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 sm:py-8">
    <h1 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Article System v0.1</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-prose text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
      Et lett referanselag for landet artikkelsystem fra sandbox. Formål: hjelpe Thomas og Vibeke med orientering og review.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-md border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-3">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700">Hva er dette</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <li>Kodet, gjenbrukbar artikkelstruktur (ikke ny designrunde).</li>
        <li>Visual source of truth: <code class="font-mono text-xs">/no/sandbox/article-master</code>.</li>
        <li>Innhold: tokens, komponenter, stylesheet og page recipe.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-600">
        VIS er referanseflate. Oppgaveflyt/backlog ligger fortsatt i GitHub Projects og issue-laget.
      </p>
    </section>

    <nav class="mt-6 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <a href={`${base}vis/system/article/foundations`} class="rounded border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">
        Foundations
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}vis/system/article/components`} class="rounded border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">
        Components
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}vis/system/article/templates`} class="rounded border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">
        Template
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}vis/system/article/changelog`} class="rounded border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">
        Changelog / status
      </a>
    </nav>
  </main>
</PrototypeLayout>
